<p style="margin: 0px;">
Every year, Bank of America associates volunteer thousands of hours to more than 3,000 nonprofit organizations. To honor those who give their time and service to causes important to them, and to demonstrate our commitment to improving our communities, the Bank of America Charitable Foundation awards grants to nonprofit organizations of up to $500 per associate each calendar year. 
</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px;">
Unrestricted grants are made in associates' names to any eligible nonprofit organization for which an associate has committed at least 50 volunteer hours within a calendar year. And, Bank of America associates also earn personal awards and recognition for their volunteer service.
</p>
